{"tid":2049130,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求Cold Call撚心理陰影面積","createTime":"2020-06-03T08:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T08:16:11.000Z","uid":25345,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"607764d651e2d320d164ba3bb1b83429b812c912","tid":2049130,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"次次聽到都好積極同好好禮貌咁既聲，但好快就比人ｃｕｔ線<br />\n不停重覆咁既過程，心理健康變成點？"},{"pid":"bed560a83d1262485a994bf966124a4a4e5e5c00","tid":2049130,"uid":139613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"近排唔知做乜撚事日日打幾個Cold Call嚟<br />\n我已經連聽都廢事聽 我警告你<br />\n咪撚再打嚟"},{"pid":"cac3e91be9ce048303179bc542b8ee8e91983575","tid":2049130,"uid":201056,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦你<br />\n原來就係你條仆街日日打黎煩鳩我"},{"pid":"9bf61f29ed22a2496214ec7df05336bb0d16c08f","tid":2049130,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"死全家啦"},{"pid":"2d3d5f6fd0cd8de725af351e6e0edfb2afcf4881","tid":2049130,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bed560a83d1262485a994bf966124a4a4e5e5c00","tid":2049130,"uid":139613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"近排唔知做乜撚事日日打幾個Cold Call嚟<br />\n我已經連聽都廢事聽 我警告你<br />\n咪撚再打嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我都想講<br />\n呢排好密<br />\n打到夜晚都有..."},{"pid":"2096ac0e90092af70612889ff99d24a794d88edd","tid":2049130,"uid":78383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"cut線唔好咩？好過屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5c3079f116054bcf04d0729e1491242d58598e","tid":2049130,"uid":17279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"我都想知佢地長期咁樣聽落去會唔會抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07ad9477574a51c0b71f092eb54e8c2ec0a67dc","tid":2049130,"uid":344615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"冇 cut線幾開心，唔洗講落去<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過"},{"pid":"ac777b2ce3ec75202ae92e5d1611b73838a73e3e","tid":2049130,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"唔好cut線，由呢班人渣慢慢自話自說"},{"pid":"d6e42983bdc4c80ed912ec03e60cf6acefab52a5","tid":2049130,"uid":102855,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:11:11.000Z","msg":"好多年前我都做過2日cold call, 記憶深刻, 因為返工第2日已經忍唔住要quit<br />\n<br />\n仲記得個call centre主管一開場就話有record記錄你每日打左幾多個call, 如果一日打唔足某數目嘅call就好似要照肺咁, 當時第一感覺就好差, 然後工作內容係幫電訊商sell增值服務, 佢有份稿教你點應對, 重點都係喺對方想拒絕但唔係好識say no嘅人時點夾佢落搭, 果兩日我成功左d case不過真係頂唔順果種好似夾鳩人落搭嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\nsell嘅增值服務無記錯係d 濕鳩串流音樂定網上音樂平台, 一開頭會係咁講畀個免費務你, 可以馬上幫你登記, 最後傾好晒先同你講個務服務係免費一個月, 之後你唔主動cut就要收費, 仲記得有個成功嘅call對方應該係一個新移民阿姐, 去到最後佢聽到一個月後要收費其實明顯想卻步, 但係佢因為唔識得拒絕人最後好似好唔情願咁接受左個服務, 我成日覺得係個阿姐果一下遲疑唔情願嘅但又唔好意思say no嘅反應令我有罪疚感而要即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f535bc35c80b6c2994317f3c7696e007d065fcda","tid":2049130,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"聽常我都即刻收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cfe716c656ee627784b3c6f9c9102d865b6a3e","tid":2049130,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"通常都等佢up完一大輪先撚到佢自己收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04781d750f475e40c84337ba8dd911807925f733","tid":2049130,"uid":181341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"其實講慣講熟克服左怕羞既第一步，我覺得都ok易做"},{"pid":"d674b9b480db012ef7ec50c01a8a27b930c97bef","tid":2049130,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"轉工啦<br />\n依份工神憎鬼厭"},{"pid":"4a57efc34dabdfa51e662906968661bb2121d56b","tid":2049130,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"好心情就聽都唔聽cut你線，心情唔好我會一接聽就屌"},{"pid":"de9d67a428273532ce0e4fe303d085b967c981c2","tid":2049130,"uid":106634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"cold call都未算最辛苦，做過上門洗樓逐家撳門鐘嗰啲，真係賤過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286f2fc16594ef40a17bd64b99b16fea3ab1c780","tid":2049130,"uid":13767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9d67a428273532ce0e4fe303d085b967c981c2","tid":2049130,"uid":106634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"cold call都未算最辛苦，做過上門洗樓逐家撳門鐘嗰啲，真係賤過隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"洗樓一定比人阻<br />\n你話公屋一句唔該入閘 fine~<br />\n但如果有痴線佬渣刀就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以為人為己都唔好做cold call狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps 屌你老母半個鍾幾個cold call<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}